  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Barista
    Text: "\xCEn fine, vrei s\u0103 bei sau nu?"
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: "Ar trebui s\u0103 vreau s\u0103 beau?"
  - Speaker: Barista
    Text: "E\u0219ti con\u0219tient\u0103 c\u0103 te afli \xEEntr-un bar, nu?"
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: "Am aflat \xEEn momentul \xEEn care am intrat, da"
  - Speaker: Barista
    Text: "C\u0103utai baia? Ei bine sunt diferen\u021Be anatomice \xEEntre plante
      \u0219i... tu"
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: 'Nu, nu caut nicio baie!!... '
